description: NIVEA Cellular Hyaluron Filler Day Cream SPF 15 features a skin-compatible combination of the cell-activating ingredients Hyaluronic Acid and Collagen Booster. The SPF15 UVA/UVB protection system helps to protect skin from UV-induced ageing, cell damage and age spots.NIVEA Cellular Filler Anti-Age Day Cream SPF 15 contains a combination of the cell-activating* ingredients Hyaluron and Bioxilift. These powerful ingredients activate the skin cells to produce their own Hyaluronic Acid and Collagen. As a result, your skin is plumper with a lifted feeling. In addition, wrinkles are filled, the skin volume is increased and contours are refined. SPF 15 and UVA/UVB protection help to protect the skin against sun-induced wrinkle formation and premature skin ageing. The skin compatibility of this day care cream has been dermatologically approved. *tested on skin cells.Quality Ingredients: formula made with Hyaluron and BioxiliftEffective Results: visibly reduces lines and wrinkles for tangibly firmer skinSPF 15: UVA/UVB protection help to protect the skin against sun-induced wrinkle formation and premature skin ageingLasting Nourishment: activates the skin cells to produce their own Hyaluronic Acid and CollagenUsage: Perfect for everyday use, even on sensitive skin types to encourage deeply nourished and smooth skinDirections: apply a generous amount to clean skin, massaging thoroughly around the face, neck, ears, and décolleté
name: Nivea Cellular Filler Anti-age Spf15 Day Cream Moisturiser 50ml
